This rating is for the presentation, the material ranks 4 stars. I bought this for Get Out Of My Room as I already own the other 2 films on DVD. The 3 titles are on 1 side of a single DVD with expected compression consequences. My VHS copy of Get Out Of My Room actually looks better than the copy on this disc and likewise Next Move & Born In East L.A. also look much worse than their prior DVD releases. Fail.

What better way to spend a cold winter day but watching a Cheech and Chong.  Two full movies, Cheech and Chongs Next movie with both Cheech and Chong, Born in East LA  with just Cheech Marin, and then a funny documentary Get Out of My Room.  Two very funny movies with the likes of comedians we may never see again in our lifetime. If your a baby boomer, you of course remember these gut busting funny movies.  Not sure if the fact it brings back memories, or just that they are among the best comedy duos in our culture.  There are three movies on one disc with no special features, commercials, or previews of other movies. Pop it in your DVD player, let it roll, and laugh out loud.......dont forget the munchies.
